Stockholm syndrome.

16:56.848 --> 16:59.351
It's where the victim...

16:59.383 --> 17:02.086
feels a connection or maybe
love towards their captor,

17:02.120 --> 17:04.622
no matter how traumatic
the experience was.

17:04.655 --> 17:06.589
