protect him or her.

17:06.624 --> 17:08.593
I'm still her mother.

17:08.626 --> 17:10.627
Yes you are.

17:13.164 --> 17:16.468
The goal is to bring her home.

17:16.501 --> 17:18.770
So I'll be spending a few
hours a day with Lauren

17:18.801 --> 17:22.406
