here, Mrs. Daly.

17:26.411 --> 17:29.014
Yeah... Right.

17:31.549 --> 17:32.751
Mrs. Daly.

17:34.618 --> 17:35.820
Mrs. Daly.

17:37.422 --> 17:39.024
Call me, Marie.

17:47.831 --> 17:50.601
Hey, bro, been looking
