-Thank you.

27:41.657 --> 27:45.495
So, bring me up to
speed on the details.

27:45.529 --> 27:48.465
Well she's still
not speaking...

27:48.499 --> 27:51.068
Her diet seems
to be coming along.

27:51.100 --> 27:54.338
